lgp.core.modules

Interface Module

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ComponentLoader<TComponent>, ConfigurationLoader, ConstantLoader<T>, DatasetLoader<TData>, OperationLoader<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Addition, And, BaseInstruction, BaseInstructionGenerator, BaseProgram, BaseProgramGenerator, BaseProgramTranslator, BinaryOperation, BinaryTournamentSelection, BranchOperation, ResultAggregators.BufferedResultAggregator, CsvDatasetLoader, DefaultOperationLoader, ResultAggregators.DefaultResultAggregator, Division, DoubleConstantLoader, EvolutionModel, ExclusiveOr, Exponent, FitnessContext, GenericConstantLoader, Identity, IfGreater, IfLessThanOrEqualTo, ResultAggregators.InMemoryResultAggregator, Instruction, InstructionGenerator, Models.IslandMigration, JsonConfigurationLoader, LinearCrossover, MacroMutationOperator, Models.MasterSlave, MicroMutationOperator, MultipleOutputFitnessContext, Multiplication, MutationOperator, Not, Operation, Or, Program, ProgramGenerator, ProgramTranslator, RecombinationOperator, ResultAggregator, SelectionOperator, Sine, SingleOutputFitnessContext, Models.SteadyState, Subtraction, TournamentSelection, UnaryOperation, YamlConfigurationLoader

    public Module

    A module in the LGP system.

    An implementation of interface Module can be used in the appropriate place in the system, meaning that custom modules can be built to provide custom functionality to the system.
